/**
 * Global "scrollbar"-style
 *
 * @description
 *   Styles the scrollbar globally.
 *   Currently only the "webkit" engine is supported.
 *   Provides "easy-to-personalize" css variables under the ":root" selector.
 *
 * @autor
 *   NYAAN <dev@nyaan.cat>
 *
 * @version
 *   0.1
 *
 * @url
 *   https://userstyles.org/users/466844
 *
